.SH NAME
iopi - MCP23017 interface
.SH SYNOPSIS
iopi [OPTION]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B iopi
controls the functions of the Microchip MCP23017 I2C based IO controller used on the IO Pi, IO Pi Plus or IO Pi Zero from AB Electronics UK.  If no options are specified iopi will read port 0 from I2C address 0x20.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-a ", " \-\-address =\fIBITS\fR
Set the number of bits to modify.



.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
